737
01:23:40,636 --> 01:23:41,665
That's right.

738
01:23:42,746 --> 01:23:45,527
Get these guys off so
I can get a clean shot.

739
01:23:45,528 --> 01:23:48,480
You heard the General.
Evasive maneuvers, let's go.

740
01:23:55,036 --> 01:23:59,417
Target locked.
Welcome to oblivion.

