Lindsey.  Stay with me!

745
01:25:27,289 --> 01:25:28,959
Dad.

746
01:25:29,039 --> 01:25:31,959
Please, it's over.

747
01:25:41,389 --> 01:25:44,100
Please...

748
01:25:47,140 --> 01:25:48,682
It's not.

